location.Description: Azure location in which project is created.

tags.Description: Tags provided by Azure Tagging service.

createdTimestamp.Description: Time when this project was created. Date-Time represented in ISO-8601 format.

updatedTimestamp.Description: Time when this project was last updated. Date-Time represented in ISO-8601 format.

discoveryStatus.Description: Reports whether project is under discovery. Possible values include: 'Unknown', 'NotStarted', 'InProgress', 'Completed'

customerWorkspaceId.Description: ARM ID of the Service Map workspace created by user.

customerWorkspaceLocation.Description: Location of the Service Map workspace created by user.

lastDiscoveryTimestamp.Description: Time when this project was created. Date-Time represented in ISO-8601 format. This value will be null until discovery is complete.

lastDiscoverySessionId.Description: Session id of the last discovery.

numberOfGroups.Description: Number of groups created in the project.

numberOfMachines.Description: Number of machines in the project.

numberOfAssessments.Description: Number of assessments created in the project.

lastAssessmentTimestamp.Description: Time when last assessment was created. Date-Time represented in ISO-8601 format. This value will be null until assessment is created.

provisioningState.Description: Provisioning state of the project. Possible values include: 'Accepted', 'Creating', 'Deleting', 'Failed', 'Moving', 'Succeeded'

machines.Description: List of machine names that are part of this group.

assessments.Description: List of References to Assessments created on this group.

createdTimestamp.Description: Time when this project was created. Date-Time represented in ISO-8601 format.

updatedTimestamp.Description: Time when this project was last updated. Date-Time represented in ISO-8601 format.

azureLocation.Description: Target Azure location for which the machines should be assessed. These enums are the same as used by Compute API. Possible values include: 'Unknown', 'EastAsia', 'SoutheastAsia', 'AustraliaEast', 'AustraliaSoutheast', 'BrazilSouth', 'CanadaCentral', 'CanadaEast', 'WestEurope', 'NorthEurope', 'CentralIndia', 'SouthIndia', 'WestIndia', 'JapanEast', 'JapanWest', 'KoreaCentral', 'KoreaSouth', 'UkWest', 'UkSouth', 'NorthCentralUs', 'EastUs', 'WestUs2', 'SouthCentralUs', 'CentralUs', 'EastUs2', 'WestUs', 'WestCentralUs', 'GermanyCentral', 'GermanyNortheast', 'ChinaNorth', 'ChinaEast'

azureOfferCode.Description: Offer code according to which cost estimation is done. Possible values include: 'Unknown', 'MSAZR0003P', 'MSAZR0044P', 'MSAZR0059P', 'MSAZR0060P', 'MSAZR0062P', 'MSAZR0063P', 'MSAZR0064P', 'MSAZR0029P', 'MSAZR0022P', 'MSAZR0023P', 'MSAZR0148P', 'MSAZR0025P', 'MSAZR0036P', 'MSAZR0120P', 'MSAZR0121P', 'MSAZR0122P', 'MSAZR0123P', 'MSAZR0124P', 'MSAZR0125P', 'MSAZR0126P', 'MSAZR0127P', 'MSAZR0128P', 'MSAZR0129P', 'MSAZR0130P', 'MSAZR0111P', 'MSAZR0144P', 'MSAZR0149P', 'MSMCAZR0044P', 'MSMCAZR0059P', 'MSMCAZR0060P', 'MSMCAZR0063P', 'MSMCAZR0120P', 'MSMCAZR0121P', 'MSMCAZR0125P', 'MSMCAZR0128P', 'MSAZRDE0003P', 'MSAZRDE0044P'

azurePricingTier.Description: Pricing tier for Size evaluation. Possible values include: 'Standard', 'Basic'

azureStorageRedundancy.Description: Storage Redundancy type offered by Azure. Possible values include: 'Unknown', 'LocallyRedundant', 'ZoneRedundant', 'GeoRedundant', 'ReadAccessGeoRedundant'

scalingFactor.Description: Scaling factor used over utilization data to add a performance buffer for new machines to be created in Azure. Min Value = 1.0, Max value = 1.9, Default = 1.3.

percentile.Description: Percentile of performance data used to recommend Azure size. Possible values include: 'Percentile50', 'Percentile90', 'Percentile95', 'Percentile99'

timeRange.Description: Time range of performance data used to recommend a size. Possible values include: 'Day', 'Week', 'Month'

stage.Description: User configurable setting that describes the status of the assessment. Possible values include: 'InProgress', 'UnderReview', 'Approved'

currency.Description: Currency to report prices in. Possible values include: 'Unknown', 'USD', 'DKK', 'CAD', 'IDR', 'JPY', 'KRW', 'NZD', 'NOK', 'RUB', 'SAR', 'ZAR', 'SEK', 'TRY', 'GBP', 'MXN', 'MYR', 'INR', 'HKD', 'BRL', 'TWD', 'EUR', 'CHF', 'ARS', 'AUD', 'CNY'

azureHybridUseBenefit.Description: AHUB discount on windows virtual machines. Possible values include: 'Unknown', 'Yes', 'No'

discountPercentage.Description: Custom discount percentage to be applied on final costs. Can be in the range [0, 100].

confidenceRatingInPercentage.Description: Confidence rating percentage for assessment. Can be in the range [0, 100].

sizingCriterion.Description: Assessment sizing criterion. Possible values include: 'PerformanceBased', 'AsOnPremises'

pricesTimestamp.Description: Time when the Azure Prices were queried. Date-Time represented in ISO-8601 format.

createdTimestamp.Description: Time when this project was created. Date-Time represented in ISO-8601 format.

updatedTimestamp.Description: Time when this project was last updated. Date-Time represented in ISO-8601 format.

monthlyComputeCost.Description: Monthly compute cost estimate for the machines that are part of this assessment as a group, for a 31-day month.

monthlyBandwidthCost.Description: Monthly network cost estimate for the machines that are part of this assessment as a group, for a 31-day month.

monthlyStorageCost.Description: Monthly storage cost estimate for the machines that are part of this assessment as a group, for a 31-day month.

status.Description: Whether the assessment has been created and is valid. Possible values include: 'Created', 'Updated', 'Running', 'Completed', 'Invalid'

numberOfMachines.Description: Number of assessed machines part of this assessment.
